			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "The following table lists all field types and their core characteristics:"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20260613155453-ga53qn2",
			"Type": "NodeTable",
			"Data": "| Field Type | Use Case | Sortable | Filterable | Aggregatable | Special Template Suffix |\n|---------|---------|--------|--------|--------|------------|\n| Text | Titles, descriptions, arbitrary text | √ | √ | × | — |\n| Number | Amounts, quantities, ratings | √ | √ | √ | — |\n| Date | Deadlines, birthdays, creation dates | √ | √ | × | `_end` |\n| Select | Status, category, priority | √ | √ | × | — |\n| Multi-Select | Tags, multi-category | √ | √ | × | `_str` |\n| URL | External links, references | × | √ | × | — |\n| Email | Contact email | × | √ | × | — |\n| Phone | Contact phone | × | √ | × | — |\n| Checkbox | Completed/not, enabled/disabled | √ | √ | × | — |\n| Primary Key (Block) | Unique record identifier, can bind to a content block | √ | √ | × | `_created` |\n| Asset | Attachments, images, files | × | × | × | — |\n| Relation | Cross-database record relations | × | √ | × | — |\n| Rollup | Statistical calculations based on relation fields | √ | √ | √ | — |\n| Template | Auto-fill default values | × | × | × | — |\n| Created Time | Record creation time (auto) | √ | √ | × | — |\n| Updated Time | Record last modified time (auto) | √ | √ | × | — |\n| Line Number | Auto-increment sequence number | √ | √ | × | — |",
